    "description": "Grow your career with HDFC Bank! We are hiring a Risk Analyst for our Jodhpur team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout HDFC Bank:\nHDFC Bank is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with HDFC Bank!",
